name: stream-evaluation
notes: Digital representation of the map accompanying the "Kansas stream and river fishery resource evaluation" (R.E. Moss and K. Brunson, 1981.U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service Contract No. 14-16-0006-80-063. Kansas Fish and Game Commission, Pratt). The database consists of 76 coverages, tiled by eight digit hydrologic units (HUC-8). This field assessment ranks stream and river reaches based on their actual and potential fisheries value.
